General.Name: Plexus Corp
General.Description: Plexus Corp. provides electronic manufacturing services in the United States and internationally. It offers design, develop, supply chain, new product introduction, and manufacturing solutions, as well as sustaining services. The company serves the aerospace/defense, healthcare/life sciences, industrial/commercial, and communications market sectors. Plexus Corp. was founded in 1979 and is headquartered in Neenah, Wisconsin.
